nLinux host code and manual: host_usb/\n\n## About\n\nAn app that allows secure LUKS unlocking using usb accessory mode without\ntyping your LUKS password\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nGPL-3.0 license\n\n### Security policy\n\nSecurity policy\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n63 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n3 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n1 fork\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases 1\n\nInitial stable proof of concept Latest\n\nSep 10, 2023\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Java 60.1%\n  * C++ 33.6%\n  * Shell 6.3%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
